{
  "_comment": "{{RIPER-5: Action: Created | Task: #BlazeBlog-Deploy-2025-07-13 | Time: 2025-07-13T22:00:00+08:00 | Reason: BlazeBlog Vercel部署配置 - 基于example文件创建生产环境配置 | Principle: 生产环境配置原则 - 优化性能、安全性和缓存策略 | Architecture_Note: [AR] Vercel部署配置，支持Hugo 0.147.9 + Node.js 18 | Memory_Reference: [mcp.memory] 应用Vercel部署最佳实践，确保中国大陆访问友好 | Quality_Check: [LD] 部署配置完整，安全头配置，缓存策略优化}}",
  "build": {
    "env": {
      "HUGO_VERSION": "0.147.9",
      "NODE_VERSION": "18",
      "HUGO_ENV": "production"
    }
  },
  "buildCommand": "npm run build",
  "outputDirectory": "public",
  "installCommand": "npm install",
  "framework": null,
  "functions": {},
  "headers": [
    {
      "source": "/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        {
          "key": "X-Content-Type-Options",
          "value": "nosniff"
        },
        {
          "key": "X-Frame-Options",
          "value": "DENY"
        },
        {
          "key": "X-XSS-Protection",
          "value": "1; mode=block"
        },
        {
          "key": "Referrer-Policy",
          "value": "strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "/css/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        {
          "key": "Cache-Control",
          "value": "public, max-age=31536000, immutable"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "/js/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        {
          "key": "Cache-Control",
          "value": "public, max-age=31536000, immutable"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "/images/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        {
          "key": "Cache-Control",
          "value": "public, max-age=31536000, immutable"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "/icons/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        {
          "key": "Cache-Control",
          "value": "public, max-age=31536000, immutable"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "redirects": [
    {
      "source": "/index.xml",
      "destination": "/feed.xml",
      "permanent": true
    }
  ]
}
